data.description: This colonial home is located in the heart of Lafayette and offers 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, cozy large living room with fireplace, dining room, utility room, 2 car garage, in-ground swimming pool and a covered outdoor cooking area which includes a gas stove. Other highlights include backyard gate access right into Neyland Park, easy access to I-10, local schools, hospitals and grocery stores.
